n Normacot. I-, it was at the entrance of where the, the Normacot end of the M-, Mere Tunnel, you know, the, the tunnel, yes, well, our, our house was, was there, and of course, er, after short time we got a house at Stoke.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12146635 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8024581\charrsid13051004 How old were you when you moved there?
