 think I must have been one of the naughty boys because I know that, er, myself and a-, another boy, we were taken to the headmistress for our behaviour. Anyhow, of course, I, I overcome that, and, er, then very shortly after, we, we moved, we moved to No
r
macot, and of course we were there, er, my father, er, he w-, he was a, an oven fireman, and, er, he was on, er, the Longton Town Council, that was before the Federation, you see, and, er, of course he, he died w- when I was, er, I should be about 11, mm,
 and, er, of course, I just, er, we, mother and I lived together, and, er, of course I was, I went to school there, and then, er, I left there to go, er, start, I started work at John Ainsley's, and ..
