w pre-, I saw pretty well of them, yes, mm. Of course, er, my brother, he was a big Stoke fan, and, and, er, as small as I was, er, for a time we lived down the Campbell Road and our backs came almost to the, to the ground of Stoke, and of course I used t
o go and meet him and he used to take me on, as a child, in, in this stand sort of thing, mm.
