 mm, and, er, at one time, of course, we used to, we used, the children used to pay the pennies, and we used to have a band from the, er, er, school at Wellington, reformatory school, we used to have this band, and then of course they used to have the ord
inary racing and what-not sort of thing, you see, at the field. We used to go as far as Weston Coyney, if you know where that is, mm, mm.
