ne occasion, er, it was, it was, er, where we, where we lived in}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5579679\charrsid13051004  ? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8024581\charrsid13051004 
Road, across the way there used to be a small piece of spare land, what we called the Chapel Field and we used to, we used to play on that, and of course, one, one day I, I must have fell i
n the trap of smoking, and, er, one, er, one of the neighbours' children went and told my father that I'd been smoking, and of course, he came across on this field and and he booted my bottom, and made me go to, go to bed for it, so they were strict over 
some things, you see, mm.
