\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12146635 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8024581\charrsid13051004 Would you have stopped on at school, if you'd had any opportunity?
